column5: Anyone knows any web link to a lake map of Lake Scugog? Trying to see how deep I'm fishing and what the structures are like in that lake. Thanks
well there aint any real structure  nothing much to see on a map  here is one  http://i542.photobucket.com/albums/gg427/T...ogtopope9-1.jpg
anglersatlas.com has one of scugog that you can download (pdf format). You'll have to create an account first.
I got this map from that anglersatlas.com web site, save you the trouble of making a account.
